title: #92Noon! PJ Fleck bookends the show!
description: Gophers football coach PJ Fleck was "ELITE" during his opening segment chat with PA today, so we replayed it to close the show. Gleeman makes his weekly appearance during the final hour as well. A lot of calls and takes throughout a hot Tuesday.
